f(n,2)=\sum_{i=1}^{n-2}f(i,1)=\sum_{i=1}^{n-2}(i-1)=\sum_{i=0}^{n-3}i=\frac{(n-3)(n-2)}2=\binom{n-2}2\;,
f(n,k)=\binom{n-k}k\;.\tag{2}
